f the international conference on the study of political thought and a fellow of the national forum on the future of liberal education last modified friday march 2 2012 2 58pm secondary links stanford home school of humanities and science contact login stanford university department of political science encina hall west suite 100 stanford california 94305 6044 phone 650 723 1806 fax 650 723 1808
